---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Refactoring Digital Garden | Dar1an" description="重构我的数字花园">
  <article class="blog-post">
    <header class="post-header">
      <div class="post-date">2023.08.01</div>
      <h1 class="post-title">
        <span class="en">Refactoring Digital Garden</span>
        <span class="cn">重构我的数字花园</span>
      </h1>
    </header>

    <div class="post-content">
      <p>数字花园（Digital Garden）是一个不断生长、迭代的知识管理系统。与博客不同，它更注重想法的演进过程，而不是最终成品。</p>

      <h2>为什么选择 Astro？</h2>
      <p>在重构我的数字花园时，我选择了 Astro 作为技术栈。原因如下：</p>
      <ul>
        <li>零 JS 默认，页面加载极快</li>
        <li>支持 Markdown 和 MDX，写作体验好</li>
        <li>可以混合使用 React、Vue 等框架</li>
        <li>静态生成，部署简单</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>技术栈选择</h2>
      <p>Astro + Cloudflare Pages 的组合，既保证了开发体验，又实现了全球 CDN 加速。</p>
    </div>

    <footer class="post-footer">
      <a href="/blog/" class="back-link">
        ← <span class="en">Back to Blog</span>
        <span class="cn">返回博客列表</span>
      </a>
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .blog-post {
    padding: 140px 10% 50px;
    padding-left: 140px;
    min-height: 100vh;
    width: 100%;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .post-header {
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .post-content {
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: #ccc;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  .post-content p,
  .post-content h2,
  .post-content ul {
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  .post-date {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .post-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .post-title .cn {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .post-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5em;
  }

  .post-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin: 2em 0 1em;
    color: var(--text-main);
  }

  .post-content ul {
    margin: 1em 0 1.5em 2em;
    list-style: disc;
  }

  .post-content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5em;
  }

  .post-footer {
    margin-top: 60px;
    padding-top: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: var(--text-main);
  }

  .back-link .cn {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .blog-post {
      padding: 100px 5% 100px;
      padding-left: 5%;
    }

    .post-title {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
    }

    .post-title .cn {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .post-content p,
    .post-content h2,
    .post-content ul {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>